@node History

@{B} History @{UB}


V1.0  10-Oct-95

- First release.



V1.1  15-Nov-95

- Fixed some problems in opening printer
  and in sending printer command.



V2.0  10-Feb-2001

- Full software rework.

- Printer dump routine rework.



V2.1  17-Feb-2001

- Added a 'Wait' window.

- Fixed some bug on computing dimension of AirFoil.

- Added a dashed line on cartesian zero.

- Added the localization.



V2.2  03-Mar-2001

- Now the points number is free between top and bottom side.

- Added the pitch line control.

- Added the FormFeed option.

- First Public release.



V2.3  30-Oct-2001

- Fix a problem that stop the normal execution of AFoil
  due to the impossibility to allocate the requested RAM resource.

- Added the possibility to print on more A4 sheet.

- Added the indication of the number of page in printing.

- Modify the Catalog file (v2.3).


@endnode
